topic.title: WOMEN WITH FIRST OFFERED APPOINTMENT WITHIN 36 MONTHS OF PREVIOUS SCREEN (PERCENTAGE)
topic.shortdesc: WOMEN WITH FIRST OFFERED APPOINTMENT WITHIN 36 MONTHS OF PREVIOUS SCREEN (PERCENTAGE) is the percentage of eligible women in a NHS Breast Screening Programme whose first offered Breast Screening invitation is within 36 months of their previous Breast Screening test.
